channel.title: My Project! Looking For A Team!
channel.description:
Hey Everyone! I am looking for a team. I want to make a silab version. I am starting from testscape but i am stripping all the retarded stuff it has, right now by myself.
I am looking for at least a 5 man team. -Project Manager/Owner (Filled - Me) -Head Coder/Coder (Open) -Dedicated hoster/Server box (Open) -Website Builder (Open) -Client Coder (Open)
I know there is no name to the server or the project. I believe thats what the group should decide on. I am going to set up a ftp server only for the members of my team. This will allow them to access the files and post updates frequently.
I prefer that you have a microphone for the computer. [/COLOR]We will be using a program called Teamspeak for our discussion. You must have a yahoo or msn/hotmail.
